              <h3 class="line-bottom mt-20 line-height-1"><span class="text-uppercase text-white">FAQ On Law & General Awareness</span></h3>
              <div id="accordion1" class="panel-group accordion">
                <div class="panel">
                  <div class="panel-title"> <a class="active" data-parent="#accordion1" data-toggle="collapse" href="#accordion11" aria-expanded="true"> <span class="open-sub"></span> What is the difference between a bill, a law and an act?</a> </div>
                  <div id="accordion11" class="panel-collapse collapse in" role="tablist" aria-expanded="true">
                    <div class="panel-content">
                      <p>If our government want to make law on a particular subject then a bill is introduced in parliament after getting the approval of both houses of parliament, the bill is sent for the assent of president.<br> <a href="https://qr.ae/pGEbyv">...View more</a></p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel">
                  <div class="panel-title"> <a data-parent="#accordion1" data-toggle="collapse" href="#accordion12" class="" aria-expanded="true"> <span class="open-sub"></span> If you could reshape the Indian government system and laws, what and how would you do so?</a> </div>
                  <div id="accordion12" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tablist" aria-expanded="true">
                    <div class="panel-content">
                      <p>The objective of our government is to establish a welfare state where fruits of development should reach the poorest. We want to establish a socialistic society having less disparity of income <br> <a href="https://qr.ae/pGEbyS">...View more</a></p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel">
                  <div class="panel-title"> <a data-parent="#accordion1" data-toggle="collapse" href="#accordion13" class="" aria-expanded="true"> <span class="open-sub"></span> Which country has the most competent government, and why?</a> </div>
                  <div id="accordion13" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tablist" aria-expanded="true">
                    <div class="panel-content">
                      <p>The democratic countries of Europe & American continent are having decent governments like of France, Germany, Sweden, Britain, US, Spain etc.<br> <a href="https://qr.ae/pGEbKI">...View more</a></p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel">
                  <div class="panel-title"> <a data-parent="#accordion1" data-toggle="collapse" href="#accordion14" class="" aria-expanded="true"> <span class="open-sub"></span> Are the information under the Official Secrets Act always inaccessible to the public? Is RTI applicable?</a> </div>
                  <div id="accordion14" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tablist" aria-expanded="true">
                    <div class="panel-content">
                      <p>Right to Information is a statutory right given by our parliament in 2005 to ensure transparency, accountability and efficiency in the working of our government.<br> <a href="https://qr.ae/pGEbKo">...View more</a></p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="panel">
                  <div class="panel-title"> <a data-parent="#accordion1" data-toggle="collapse" href="#accordion15" class="" aria-expanded="true"> <span class="open-sub"></span> Should Rajya Sabha be abolished and reform the entire colonial legislative system in Bharat?</a> </div>
                  <div id="accordion15" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tablist" aria-expanded="true">
                    <div class="panel-content">
                      <p>India is federal country. We have a federal constitution. Our country consists of 28 states and 8 UTs. One of the mandatory feature of federalism is bicameralism in which the upper house of parliament have representatives of states. <br> <a href="https://qr.ae/pGEbKl">...View more</a></p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
